music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">Porto</a> this summer.</p><p> Meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bon-iver-drops-new-singles-if-only-i-could-wait-featuring-danielle-haim-and-walk-home-3846459">Danielle Haim has teamed up with Bon Iver on his new single &#39;If Only I Could Wait&#39;</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haims-danielle-on-new-single-everybodys-trying-to-figure-me-out-writing-it-has-gotten-me-through-some-hard-times-3851714">HAIM&#39;s Danielle on new single &#39;Everybody&#39;s Trying to Figure Me Out&#39;: “Writing it has gotten me through some hard times”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
